  "title": "no-store-subscription",
  "contents": "\n\n\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/projects/ngrx.io/content/guide/eslint-plugin/rules/no-store-subscription.md?message=docs%3A%20describe%20your%20change...\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  </div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n<h1 id=\"no-store-subscription\">no-store-subscription<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/eslint-plugin/rules/no-store-subscription#no-store-subscription\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p>Using the <code>async</code> pipe is preferred over <code>store</code> subscription.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Type</strong>: suggestion</li>\n<li><strong>Recommended</strong>: Yes</li>\n<li><strong>Fixable</strong>: No</li>\n<li><strong>Suggestion</strong>: No</li>\n<li><strong>Requires type checking</strong>: No</li>\n<li><strong>Configurable</strong>: No</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Everything above this generated, do not edit -->\n<!-- MANUAL-DOC:START -->\n<h2 id=\"rule-details\">Rule Details<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/eslint-plugin/rules/no-store-subscription#rule-details\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>Examples of <strong>incorrect</strong> code for this rule:</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nngOnInit() {\n  this.store.select(selectedItems).subscribe(items => {\n    this.items = items;\n  })\n}\n</code-example>\n<p>Examples of <strong>correct</strong> code for this rule:</p>\n<!-- prettier-ignore -->\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n// in code\nselectedItems$ = this.store.select(selectedItems)\n\n// in template\n{{ selectedItems$ | async }}\n</code-example>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - guide/eslint-plugin/rules/no-store-subscription#no-store-subscription\n - guide/eslint-plugin/rules/no-store-subscription#rule-details\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/projects/ngrx.io/content/guide/eslint-plugin/rules/no-store-subscription.md?message=docs%3A%20describe%20your%20change...\n-->"
}